urchased, other than in India where such benefits can be availed in all the cities within India.</p>\n\n<p>c. The Discount shall be extended only if the Zomato Pro member makes payment towards the Bill Value via the Zomato Platform.</p>\n\n<p>d. You will be responsible to pay the Partner Restaurant(s) all costs and charges payable for all the other items for which you have placed an Order and which are not covered under the Discount.</p>\n\n<p>e. There is no limit on the number of times the Discount can be availed in a day.</p>\n\n<p>f. The Discount shall not be applicable on tobacco and related products.</p>\n\n<p>g. The Partnered Restaurant(s) offering Zomato Pro for home delivery may differ from Partnered Restaurants offering Zomato Pro for dine out.</p>\n\n<p>h. The term of your Zomato Pro membership shall be subject to the membership plan opted by You.</p>\n\n<p>i .Zomato Pro - Dine in<br />\nWhile availing Zomato Pro benefits on dine in, following terms and conditions shall be specifically applicable to Zomato Pro members:</p>\n\n<p>i. Upon fulfilment of payment of the Bill Value via the Zomato Platform, You will be required to show the payment confirmation to the Partner Restaurant.</p>\n\n<p>ii. cannot be clubbed during the same visit.</p>\n\n<p>iii. Zomato Pro members are required to be present at the Partner Restaurant when availing the Discount.</p>\n\n<p>iv. The Discount cannot be clubbed with any ongoing Partner Restaurant offers or on menu items which are being sold on discount except items sold on maximum retail price (MRP).</p>\n\n<p>v. The Discount extended by the Merchant shall be valid irrespective of the number of people seated on the table.</p>\n\n<p>j.&nbsp;Zomato Pro for Online Ordering:</p>\n\n<p>i. As a member of Zomato Pro in India, you can avail Discount on Order placed by You from partnered Restaurants.</p>\n\n<p>ii. The Discount cannot be clubbed with any other offers or discounts or deals extended by the Partnered Restaurant or Zomato o