ease note that some of the Nutrition Products may be suitable for certain ages only. You should check the Nutrition Product you are ordering and read its description, if provided, prior to placing your order. Zomato shall not be liable in the event the Nutrition Product ordered by You does not meet your dietary or any other requirements and/or restrictions.</p>\n\n<p>xxii. While placing an order you shall be required to provide certain details, including without limitation, contact number and delivery address. You agree to take particular care when providing these details and warrant that these details are accurate and complete at the time of placing an Order. By providing these details, you express your acceptance to Zomato&#39;s terms and privacy policies.</p>\n\n<p>xxiii. You or any person instructed by you shall not resell the Nutrition Products purchased via the Zomato Platform.</p>\n\n<p>xxiv. Delivery periods quoted at the time of ordering are approximate only and may vary.</p>\n\n<p>xxv. All offers or discounts or deals on Nutrition Products shall be for limited stocks and limited period(s). Zomato reserves the right to alter, extend or withdraw, as the case may be, any offers or discounts or promotions extended by Zomato at any time without giving any prior notice to the Customers. In such cases, such revision will be updated on the Zomato Platform accordingly.</p>\n\n<p>xxvi. Any personal promo code issued to the Customer can only be used by the Customer subject to such terms and conditions set forth by Zomato from time to time.</p>\n\n<p>xxvii. Contact Us: For any further query with regard to Zomato Nutrition, you may contact us via in app chat support or write to us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:nutrition.support@zomato.com\" target=\"_blank\">nutrition.support@zomato.com</a>.</p>\n\n<p>b. Cancellation, Return and Refund:</p>\n\n<p>i.&nbsp;Cancellation by Customer:&nbsp;In the event of request for cancellation of the order before its delivery, Zomato may accept the request for cancellation of the order and refund the amount up to the Order Value to the Customer within a reasonable period of time, provided that it shall be the sole discretion of Zomato to accept or reject the request for cancellation of order. Zomato shall have the right to charge a cancellation fee from the customer if the merchant is charging a cancellation fee from Zomato.</p>\n\n<p>ii.&nbsp;Cancellation by Zomato:&nbsp;There may be cases where Zomato is either unable to accept the order or cancels the order, due to any reasons including without limitation, technical errors, non-availability of the Nutrition Product, or non-availability of the desired quantity of the Nutrition Product ordered by the Customer, non-availability of the service, inaccuracies or errors in pricing information, inaccurate particulars such as contact number, address, etc. provided by the Customer, unresponsive Customer, etc. In such cases, You accept and acknowledge that Zomato reserves the right, at its sole discretion, to refuse or cancel any order for any reason whatsoever, without assigning any reason to the Customer, and the Customer shall accept and undertake that the same is acceptable and he/ she/ it will not contest/ raise any dispute on the same.</p>\n\n<p>iii. If the order is cancelled after payment has been charged and the Customer is eligible for the refund of the Order Value or any part thereof in accordance with the policies of Zomato, the said amount will be reversed in the Customer&rsquo;s account of the same source. In the event the Customer has provided incorrect particulars, e.g., contact number, delivery address etc., or that the Customer was unresponsive, not reachable or unavailable for fulfillment of the services offered to them, the Customer will not be eligible for any refunds.</p>\n\n<p>iv. Zomato&#39;s decision of cancellation of order shall be final and Zomato shall not be liable for such cancellation(s) whatsoever;</p>\n\n<p>v.&nbsp;Refund or Replacement:&nbsp;In certain cases, Zomato may offer replacement or refund, as it may in its sole discretion decide, on the Nutrition Products ordered by the Customer via the Zomato Platform, and the same shall be subject to terms and conditions as detailed below. For clarity, replacement or refund shall be subject to the Customer returning the Nutrition Product delivered to them.</p>\n\n<p>vi. Replacement or Refund of the Nutrition Product can be made in cases where the Nutrition Product(s) delivered to the Customer do not match the Order; or the Nutrition Product(s) delivered are past or near their expiry date as per applicable law ; or Nutrition Products which were damaged (includes unsealed) during delivery or wrong order is delivered. Please note, do not accept the delivery of any Product which has a tampered seal. If after opening the Nutrition Product package, the Product is found to be damaged, ther resolution will be provided without Merchant(s)&rsquo; permission, unless otherwise provided under the applicable law.</p>\n\n<p>vii. Zomato shall offer replacement or refund of the Nutrition Product only if the Customer raises a concern with the customer care/chat support within 14 days from the receipt of the Nutrition Product. Further, the Customer shall not be allowed to raise more than one return request per order on the Zomato Platform. The return request may be for multiple products associated with the same order.</p>\n\n<p>viii. You may initiate the return request via the in app chat support or you may write to us at&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:nutrition.support@zomato.com\" target=\"_blank\">nutrition.support@zomato.com</a>.</p>\n\n<p>ix. Upon receiving the return request, Zomato shall first verify the nature of the request, and may request image(s) of Nutrition Product mentioned in the return request to validate the authenticity of the return request. Once verified that the claim is genuine, Zomato may require the Customer to return the Nutrition Product to such