ucts shall not be eligible for a return or replacement under cases where the Nutrition Product has been opened, used or disfigured; If the Product is tampered; If the packaging and/or packaging box and/or packaging seal of the Product has been tampered with; If the packaging on the Product and/or the detail page of the Product mentions that the said product is non-returnable; Any accessories/freebies supplied with the Nutrition Product are missing; If the Nutrition Product does not have serial number / UPC number/ barcode affixed, which was present at the time of acceptance of the said products by the Customer from the Delivery Partner; If any damage/defect which is not covered under the manufacturer&#39;s warranty. If the product is damaged due to misuse.&nbsp;Please note that the Nutrition Product would not be eligible for return in case of issues/claims related to allergies. The Customer should consult with a doctor/medical expert before purchasing the Nutrition Product.</p>\n\n<p>xvi. However, Zomato may accept a return request if the Nutrition Products are defective, deficient or spurious or misbranded.</p>\n\n<p>xvii. It shall be the sole discretion of Zomato to decide whether the product is eligible to be returned or not and Zomato&rsquo;s decision shall be final and binding on the Customers.</p>\n\n<p>c. Review Guidelines for Nutrition Products:&nbsp;While we welcome our Customer&rsquo;s opinion and descriptions of their experience(s), You agree and acknowledge that your reviews and photos, as well as your profile and the comments you share regarding Nutrition Products, are subject to the guidelines as detailed below:</p>\n\n<p>i. Only one review for each online order transaction for Nutrition Product can be submitted and your most recent experience counts. You may edit and update your review based on subsequent orders at any time. Please note, reviews about old Product experiences (more than 6 months old) will be deleted from the Zomato Platform.</p>\n\n<p>